title: Blazing 5 - Week 11
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 11
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and RJ Bell go over in week 11:


Houston at Baltimore

Denver at Minnesota

New York at Washington

Arizona at San Francisco

Kansas City at Los Angeles


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast
